- `research/npm-package-health/github-api.md` -- Rate limit tiers (60 unauth vs 5,000 auth), 202 retry pattern for stats/contributors and stats/commit_activity endpoints, repo endpoint fields used for scoring
- `research/npm-package-health/security-vulnerability-apis.md` -- OSV /v1/query and /v1/querybatch request shapes, ecosystem parameter for npm, graceful degradation on timeout
- `research/npm-package-health/production-concerns.md` -- Parallel fetch dependency chain (packument first then fan out), error isolation pattern (signal-level independent failure), scoped package URL encoding requirement
